#  Supabase    Postgres 500MB · Storage 1GB · 50,000 auth users · Free forever
#  Cloudinary  25GB storage · 25GB bandwidth · Auto image optimisation · Free forever
#  Vercel      Unlimited deployments · 100GB bandwidth · Free for hobby projects
#  GA4         Free forever (Google Analytics)
